 POLICE in Delta State have arrested a man for allegedly raping a 13-year-old girl in Ovwian, Udu council area of the state. The suspect, 60, was reportedly arrested by a team from the Ovwian/Aladja Police Division. According to reports, the suspect allegedly defiled the teenager in his home after enticing her with some money. Police spokesman DSP Onome Onovwakpoyeya, confirmed the development on Monday, adding that the command was investigating the matter. 